31
00:01:33,570 --> 00:01:35,833
Because he's always got some guy on pushing a book about

32
00:01:35,895 --> 00:01:38,562
how everything's all going to hell, or they're going to pass a law,

33
00:01:38,736 --> 00:01:42,658
