79
00:04:37,133 --> 00:04:39,059
Damn good. Stupid bastard.

80
00:04:39,207 --> 00:04:42,290
Well, you are his editor, Doyle. Talk to him. Assign him something.

81
00:04:42,366 --> 00:04:46,021
