85
00:04:52,985 --> 00:04:54,204
I don't know what to do.

86
00:04:54,527 --> 00:04:58,675
Um, Doyle, I just finished that piece on the dissatisfaction of the faculty with the tenure system,

87
00:04:58,746 --> 00:05:01,709
