152
00:08:02,881 --> 00:08:06,015
I wore this, ironically, by the way. I was never into her. Not my thing.

153
00:08:06,092 --> 00:08:06,993
Right.

154
00:08:07,203 --> 00:08:08,124
Anything else, Kyon?

155
